OL,3,CFormer PCSO who sent sexual messages
OL,4,Cto sting Snapchat account avoids jail
OL,6,FA former Police Community Support
OL,7,FOfficer (PCSO) who thought he was
OL,8,Fsending sexualised messages to a 13-
OL,9,Fyear-old girl has avoided being sent
OL,10,Fto prison.
OL,12,FDaniel Carlson exchanged messages with
OL,13,Fa profile on social media apps,
OL,14,Fincluding Snapchat, he believed
OL,15,Fbelonged to a child, in July and
OL,16,FAugust this year, according to
OL,17,FHampshire Constabulary.
OL,19,FBut the 29-year-old was actually
OL,20,Fcommunicating with a sting account
OL,21,Foperated by a police officer.
