OL,3,CFormer PCSO who sent sexual messages
OL,4,Cto sting Snapchat account avoids jail
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,7,Fattempting to engage in sexual
OL,8,Fcommunication with a child and two
OL,9,Fcounts of attempting to cause or
OL,10,Fincite a girl aged 13 to 15 to engage
OL,11,Fin sexual activity at Bournemouth
OL,12,FCrown Court.
OL,14,FHe was sentenced to an eight-month
OL,15,Fprison term suspended for two years
OL,16,Fand ordered to complete 20
OL,17,Frehabilitation days, 200 hours of
OL,18,Funpaid work, and was placed on the sex
OL,19,Foffenders' register for 10 years.
