OL,3,CFormer PCSO who sent sexual messages
OL,4,Cto sting Snapchat account avoids jail
OL,6,FCarlson, who was previously a PCSO
OL,7,Fbased at Winchester, has since been
OL,8,Fdismissed by the force.
OL,10,FA spokesman said: "A court heard at
OL,11,Fthe start of the conversation, Carlson
OL,12,Fwas told the profile belonged to a
OL,13,Fchild, but he continued to send
OL,14,Fmessages. Among these messages were
OL,15,Frepeated offers to pay for sexually
OL,16,Fexplicit images.
OL,18,F"Bournemouth Crown Court was told the
OL,19,Fperson behind the account was actually
OL,20,Fa police officer, and not a child as
OL,21,FCarlson had believed."
