OL,3,CFormer PCSO who sent sexual messages
OL,4,Cto sting Snapchat account avoids jail
OL,6,FDeputy Chief Constable Sam de Reya
OL,7,Fsaid: "The abhorrent behaviour
OL,8,Fdisplayed by Daniel Carlson has
OL,9,Fabsolutely no place in society, let
OL,10,Falone in policing.
OL,12,F"As police officers and staff, we are
OL,13,Fentrusted with protecting the most
OL,14,Fvulnerable in our communities,
OL,15,Fparticularly children, a duty at the
OL,16,Fcore of public service and our child-
OL,17,Fcentred policing approach.
