OL,3,CFormer PCSO who sent sexual messages
OL,4,Cto sting Snapchat account avoids jail
OL,6,F"The messages Carlson sent, believing
OL,7,Fhe was engaging with a child, are
OL,8,Freprehensible and totally at odds with
OL,9,Fwhat the public rightly expect from
OL,10,Fthose working in the police service.
OL,12,F"We are out there, proactively seeking
OL,13,Fout offending against children,
OL,14,Fparticularly involving sexual
OL,15,Fcriminality, and this should send a
OL,16,Fclear message that there will be no
OL,17,Ftolerance of this from anyone.
