OL,6,F"Carlson's offending was identified,
OL,7,Finvestigated, and acted upon quickly,
OL,8,Fleading to the conviction at court and
OL,9,Fswift dismissal of a serving member of
OL,10,Fstaff.
OL,12,F"His actions do not reflect the hard
OL,13,Fwork and professionalism of the
OL,14,Fofficers, staff and volunteers, who
OL,15,Fdeliver to the highest standards every
OL,16,Fday across Hampshire & Isle of Wight
OL,17,FConstabulary.
